Package: chromVAR
Type: Package
Title: Chromatin Variation Across Regions
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2015-08-28
Authors@R: c(
    person("Alicia", "Schep", email = "aschep@stanford.edu", role = c("aut","cre")),
    person("Jason", "Buenrostro", email = "jbuenros@stanford.edu", role = "ctb"),
    person("Stanford University", role = "cph"))
Description: Determine variation in chromatin accessibility across sets of
    annotations or peaks. Designed primarily for single-cell or sparse chromatin
    accessibility, e.g. from scATAC-seq or sparse ATAC or DNAse-seq experiments.
